{"id":256344,"type":6,"name":"Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/dc/3f/256344_dxx1Y.jpg","rating":{"total":6,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":2,"6":0,"7":1,"8":2,"9":1,"10":0},"score":7},"summary":"Amazon宣布直接预订《杰克·莱恩 Jack Ryan》，首季为8集，由John Krasinski饰演主角Jack Ryan。本剧根据Tom Clancy笔下著名的CIA英雄形象改编，由Amazon和Paramount TV制作。本剧的制作团队包括 Carlton Cuse和编剧Graham Roland与Michael Bay等。主演是选角导演苦苦找寻到的。\r\n　　本剧由Cuse和Roland创作，根据Clancy的小说改编；本剧将不会是原著小说的直接改编，而是将这个CIA分析专家和侦探的角色作为原型的再创作。小说中Ryan因为一次直升机事故受伤而退伍，之后做过一段时间的投资经纪人，然后在美国海军学院谋得了一个职位，再后来进入了CIA，累官至中情局副局长，最后成为了美国总统。\r\n　　与其他经典文学或电视的形象是由演员们的表演来定义角色形象不同的是，Jack Ryan在系列电影中曾有四个不同的演员诠释过这个角色：Alec Baldwin、Harrison Ford、Ben Affleck和最近的Chris Pine。现在，Krasinski要作为新鲜血液加入这个四人组当中。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>杰克·莱恩</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>星期五</li><li><span>集数: </span>8</li><li><span>开始: </span>2018年8月31日</li><li><span>结束: </span>2018年8月31日</li><li><span>类型: </span>动作/谍战/罪案</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>电视台: </span>Amazon</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":10,"doing":1,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"美剧","count":5},{"name":"Amazon","count":2},{"name":"2018","count":1},{"name":"杰克·莱恩","count":1},{"name":"恐怖分子","count":1},{"name":"中东","count":1},{"name":"谍战","count":1},{"name":"TV","count":1},{"name":"剧情","count":1},{"name":"反恐","count":1},{"name":"Netflix","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":813424,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/813424","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":813425,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/813425","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":813426,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/813426","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":813427,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/813427","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":813428,"u